# Project context

- Full map: `docs/DOMAINS.md`
- This repo: **Burn & Build** — full desktop web product on **burnandbuilddiet.com**
- API backend: `server/` → Render (`program-creator-3tzd.onrender.com`)

Push to `main` deploys static site via GitHub Pages.

## Paths

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `/` (index.html) | Marketing landing |
| `questionnaire/` | Intake → Burn Engine → checkout handoff |
| `createyourfoodplan/` | Stripe checkout paywall |
| `program-report/` | Unified program shell (Welcome → Menu planner) |
| `menuplanner/` | Redirect → program-report page 4 |
| `server/` | Express API + SQLite (Render) |
| `contacts/` | Admin contact list |

**Product name:** Menu planner (never “meal planner” in user-facing copy).

## Print Shop (menu planner)

Five print documents, **two header templates**:

| Header | Documents |
|--------|-----------|
| **Personalized** (name + date) | Weekly meal plan, Grocery list |
| **Generic** (brand + title) | Food list, For Best Results, FAQ |

**Generic doc content is fixed** — do not ad lib or refactor copy/layout unless explicitly requested. Source data:

| Document | Data |
|----------|------|
| Food list | `data/foodListPrintout.js` + tips Q&A in `data/*TipsPrintout.js`; food names from program |
| For Best Results | `data/forBestResultsPrintout.js` |
| FAQ | `data/handbookFaqPrintout.js` |

**Generic print pipeline:** `menuplanner/js/genericPrintEngine.js` — each page is a fixed letter-size sheet (`@page margin: 0`); pagination authored in data files; opens in a new window for print (not iframe).

**Deprecated:** `pwa-burn-and-build` (archived), `gettheburnandbuildapp.com`, `/myplan/` phone app.
